Create Monetag Account
- Monetag Account
- Login Monetag Account
- Create link for marketing
- Url Shortner/ Link Shortner
- Payments Method

a. Monetag Account:
	
	1. Open Chrome Browser, type "monetag" and click on "monetag.com"
	2. click on "SIGN UP"

		Personal data
		click on "Individual"
		First name:
		Last name
		Email:
		Country/Recidents:
		City:
		Address:
		click on "Continue" button

		Wthat do you monitize:  Social traffic
		Tell us more about your audience: Facebook, Twitter, Instragram etc.
		How did you hear about us: Youtube
		What other ad networks....do you work with: adsterra
		I accept ....(click here)
		I am not a robot (click here)
		click on "Sign Up" button 

	3. Active Account:
		- open your mail account --> check "Monetag" mail and open it
		- Verify Account (click)
		- Create password to complete registration
			Password:......
			Confirm Password: ......
			click on "Finish and logi n" button 

b. Login Monetag Account
  1. Open Chrome Browser, type "monetag" and click on "monetag.com"
	2. click on "Login"
 
c. Create link for marketing: 
	- After login to "monetag.com", click on "Direct Link" menu
	- click on "+Add Direct Link" button and copy the link
 
d. Url Shortner: use to short the ads link

	- After copy the link, open chrome browser and type "url shortner free"
	- Free URL Shortner (click)
	- paste the large link in "Enter link here" and click on "Shorten URL"
	- copy short link

e. Payments Method:
	- click on "Payments" menu



 
